@startuml
title Activity Diagram - AI Shortlisting (Planned)

start
:Company runs AI shortlist;
:Frontend sends POST /api/screening/shortlist;
:Server loads applicants and job details from database;
:Server sends data to AI Screening Engine;
:AI Screening Engine evaluates candidates;
:AI Screening Engine returns scores and shortlist;
:Server stores shortlist results in database;
:Return 200 with shortlisted list;
:Frontend displays shortlist to company;
stop

@enduml
